title: Liara Roux: "Whore Of New York: A Confession"
description: Liara Roux, a sex worker and advocate for the profession in New York City, joins Michael with her memoir, "Whore of New York." Original air date 1 November 2021. The book was published on 12 October 2021.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Michael Smerconish, Liara Roux, TC Scornavacchi)
